message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper deals with visual question answering, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The method presented in the paper involves selecting relevant image regions based on text-based queries, which involves machine learning (cs.AI) and decision-making (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with finding relevant information from a large dataset.
